text: Aloisie Krongeigerová (born 1900, date of death unknown) was a Czech diver. She competed in the women's 3 metre springboard event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1900 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Czech female divers Category:Olympic divers of Czechoslovakia Category:Divers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
